    <div class="sf-Long-text" ><h4>Louise Cummins, Chief Marketing Officer</h4><div></div><div><div>Louise joined World Vision Australia in March 2022 with more than 20 years&rsquo; experience in marketing, management and organisational change. Louise has a track record of leading and mentoring her teams to produce results.</div><div>&nbsp;</div><div><p>Louise was named in the Top 50 CMO list for 2021 and was a finalist in B&amp;T&rsquo;s Best of the Best Marketer for 2021. She has served on several not-for-profit boards, including The Housing Connection, Sydney Drug Education and Counselling Centre, and has previously worked with World Vision as a consultant for VisionFund from 2006-2010.<br /></p></div><p></p></div><div></div></div>
